{"tid":349741,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[無底線]一人1xN樣奇怪習慣／變態野","createTime":"2017-08-06T17:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T18:10:42.000Z","uid":1858,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d92894ca2fc2fc085ba29087773cd1a248ad8e79","tid":349741,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:39:16.000Z","msg":"之所以叫1xN 係因為想你地最好一個個打出黎，咁就可以詳盡d<br />\n<br />\n至於無底線係歡迎咁多位巴打分享要幾奇怪／變態有幾奇怪變態層慣<br />\neg:你鍾意食屎&lt;你鍾意食人d屎&lt;你鍾意食袋鼠d屎"},{"pid":"7a7a2648a75479b9bcc729603a6885f0b8e7ee49","tid":349741,"uid":29438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:40:40.000Z","msg":"明知臭既野 特登去聞下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d390fb825d8aa6c51204f95811d6a6926f8affe4","tid":349741,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:44:05.000Z","msg":"拋磚先<br />\n平時係屋企屙屎一定會用花灑同soap 洗下個廁板先去，亦都極少可會去公廁，去親都一定會去好靚好乾淨嘅廁所，就算附近無同有野做緊都會不惜一切飛的去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b940eeac46fa45750b8368d8696551fd3af948","tid":349741,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:45:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明知臭既野 特登去聞下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過睇下件物件係咩，即係你話肥婆d汗／公廁d屎尿味個d就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"980d93f349bd532fb826b457145399dc80ee0d10","tid":349741,"uid":56199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:47:55.000Z","msg":"習慣左扮正常"},{"pid":"d2b830be71dfbd207fe1f17e5583a2a4e3b32da9","tid":349741,"uid":10256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:24:23.000Z","msg":"R完屎忽會索番陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f9b3a6cb0f59bded53442ae31ea250828c1db5","tid":349741,"uid":86943,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:56:53.000Z","msg":"鐘意self sabotage，故意令所有自己做到嘅嘢都做唔到，做人永遠要維持中下遊。"},{"pid":"87042b58e767695adb0f0842d16e9740aae2238a","tid":349741,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T19:14:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>R完屎忽會索番陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係人都會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1cba1896674dfbdd19fd0c9eefbab07dca093b9","tid":349741,"uid":1858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T19:15:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鐘意self sabotage，故意令所有自己做到嘅嘢都做唔到，做人永遠要維持中下遊。</blockquote><br />\n係人面前我或者都會，等人唔好比自己太大期望，柒左都冇咩野<br />\n<br />\n自己一個個時就唔會"},{"pid":"2d5d8833b3dcf9af298f35597114c4cdbf2944e9","tid":349741,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T19:19:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鐘意self sabotage，故意令所有自己做到嘅嘢都做唔到，做人永遠要維持中下遊。</blockquote><br />\n係人面前我或者都會，等人唔好比自己太大期望，柒左都冇咩野<br />\n<br />\n自己一個個時就唔會</blockquote><br />\n我自己一個嘅時侯從來都冇令自己失望過，但係係人面前會唔知點解做啲令自己都失望嘅事，好似同chromic depression有關"},{"pid":"757b848a01d3fa9025d3875c460f734d7e209964","tid":349741,"uid":25857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T19:21:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拋磚先<br />\n平時係屋企屙屎一定會用花灑同soap 洗下個廁板先去，亦都極少可會去公廁，去親都一定會去好靚好乾淨嘅廁所，就算附近無同有野做緊都會不惜一切飛的去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n潔癖姐 我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n急死都唔去污糟廁所"},{"pid":"92eca8a5ebdc8fcfa79584284582113014c00e0a","tid":349741,"uid":68963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T19:23:30.000Z","msg":"好鍾意聞啲手寫過底單據陣味"},{"pid":"c21f909728b0a9f841de9f60491443c902534570","tid":349741,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T19:57:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鐘意self sabotage，故意令所有自己做到嘅嘢都做唔到，做人永遠要維持中下遊。</blockquote><br />\n係人面前我或者都會，等人唔好比自己太大期望，柒左都冇咩野<br />\n<br />\n自己一個個時就唔會</blockquote><br />\n我自己一個嘅時侯從來都冇令自己失望過，但係係人面前會唔知點解做啲令自己都失望嘅事，好似同chromic depression有關</blockquote><br />\n我唔知同唔同你一樣，我係一味話唔識唔曉先，同埋就算肯定嘅野都會話：丫，會唔會係咁呢，純粹等人覺得自己唔識唔會睇得我太高。同埋自己有唔少能力都唔會同人講，係人面前都扮唔識eg彈琴"},{"pid":"e26bff67ca34ebb23bf1cfb58e78450f2993cb0d","tid":349741,"uid":1858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T20:06:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拋磚先<br />\n平時係屋企屙屎一定會用花灑同soap 洗下個廁板先去，亦都極少可會去公廁，去親都一定會去好靚好乾淨嘅廁所，就算附近無同有野做緊都會不惜一切飛的去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n潔癖姐 我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n急死都唔去污糟廁所</blockquote><br />\n正確黎講我係直頭強逼症，潔癖只係一少環，有時洗完手隻手唔小心掂到其他野（都必係污糟野）都會逼自己再洗過，重覆洗十次手都唔係罕有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做野有少少出錯都要再做過，一定要啱曬為止"},{"pid":"d67f354f7556be7d40d20a278ae3a24a470815e0","tid":349741,"uid":82742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T20:07:17.000Z","msg":"食鼻屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898e9cf23ca16f31b60436a8886b74e1793c13